pillars.name: Search

reports.name: Trends
reports.description: This report will highlight your ad performance over time. Optimize your advertising by understanding and driving these trends.

reports.name: Seasonality
reports.description: See the underlying seasonality of your advertising to understand performance. Are your ads performing well on Sundays? Find out.

sections.name: User Funnel
sections.description: See the user behavior that drives you advertising performance. Find the targets that under and over perform and find bottlenecks in your conversion funnel.

reports.name: Conversion Rate
reports.description: Track how targets are moving from impression to click to conversion. Segment by device, network, or audience to find where you need to optimize.

sections.name: Opportunities
sections.description: Take immediate action to optimize your marketing spend and improve results. These opportunity reports show you what to stop doing and what to do more of.

reports.name: Worst Performing Ads
reports.description: Quickly find the ads that need to be paused or have their bid lowered.

reports.name: Worst Performing Keywords
reports.description: See performance of your individual ads with a focus on underperforming, expensive creatives. Quickly find the ads that need to be paused or have their bid lowered.

reports.name: Budget Constrained
reports.description: See performance of your individual keywords with a focus on underperforming, expensive targets. Quickly find the keywords that need to be paused or have their bid lowered.

reports.name: Bid Optimization
reports.description: See the performance of targeting criteria. Quickly uncover high performance targets to increase bids and areas for improvement.

pillars.description: These reports dive into your Adwords to find ways to increase the ROI of your marketing spend. Use Opportunities to find quick wins, refine your targets using the Performance trend reports, or discover which audiences are falling off your funnel.
